{
  "texts": [
    "Key lemmas include \"actor,\" \"film,\" \"movie,\" \"entertainment,\" and \"TID.\"",
    "Discussions highlight the transformative possibilities of deep fake in the movie industry, envisioning scenarios where any actor can be seamlessly replaced or chosen post-production.",
    "Examples are provided, such as the recreation of iconic movie scenes with different actors.",
    "TID (The Indian deep_faker) is introduced as a prominent player in creating artificial intelligence-generated content for social media.",
    "The ethical implications of deep fake in entertainment are acknowledged, with perspectives on its positive and negative aspects."
  ]
}